{"tid":2028460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"27號國歌法 28號國安法","createTime":"2020-05-21T23:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T08:36:02.000Z","uid":146917,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"80dc55c772b5c7a2662e4884238b6b03b7169799","tid":2028460,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T23:18:21.000Z","msg":"應該唔係巧合 係有計劃準備好<br />\n而最快真正立法就係六個月後<br />\n中共好明顯係襯其他國家處理緊肺炎加快控制香港<br />\n亦有可能人大會議本身都會會係林鄭完任前落實23條<br />\n只不過係肺炎拖延左開會時間<br />\n更有可能聽左攬炒巴話會同其他國家結成姐妹城市<br />\n即 台灣同香港 所以口交部再出文對蔡英文當選深表遺憾<br />\n<br />\n對我地目前影響有兩大阻攔<br />\n1. 黑警部署<br />\n唔多講 亦都係我哋最大阻礙嘅事 <br />\n我地仲未破解到佢地行動<br />\n<br />\n2. 攬炒<br />\n好多人都唔想攬炒 <br />\n<br />\n如果國安法真係成功 <br />\n就唔會有咁多人有對呢件事有迴響 吹雞岀黎<br />\n而唔係開心攬炒<br />\n暫時未睇到外資有咩行動 往往商人最快可以部署<br />\n所以可以暫時睇下情況<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遊行係冇用 行動最實際<br />\n從來口號都唔係口號 係做先好講"},{"pid":"722d32367dae48e1fee6f8fef3f91f7c1bffa8e0","tid":2028460,"uid":16676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T23:33:58.000Z","msg":"林鄭當初上任承諾任內唔會就23條咨詢同立法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ca283dfa88f626b8eb4e69b86f9c58c93ef456","tid":2028460,"uid":86453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"722d32367dae48e1fee6f8fef3f91f7c1bffa8e0","tid":2028460,"uid":16676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T23:33:58.000Z","msg":"林鄭當初上任承諾任內唔會就23條咨詢同立法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T23:36:59.000Z","msg":"柒婆講嘅野仲可信？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936ed740d4a0fb99322cfeec49d0f3f1115b494b","tid":2028460,"uid":146917,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"722d32367dae48e1fee6f8fef3f91f7c1bffa8e0","tid":2028460,"uid":16676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T23:33:58.000Z","msg":"林鄭當初上任承諾任內唔會就23條咨詢同立法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T23:38:50.000Z","msg":"佢當時上任承諾都話有大量人反對佢就會問責下台啦<br />\n你仲信佢？"},{"pid":"7c03bb973f2f1c91002e2135fb105c1ac1eb3ff5","tid":2028460,"uid":47775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"722d32367dae48e1fee6f8fef3f91f7c1bffa8e0","tid":2028460,"uid":16676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T23:33:58.000Z","msg":"林鄭當初上任承諾任內唔會就23條咨詢同立法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T23:42:09.000Z","msg":"信佢講野果啲智商應該低過30"},{"pid":"03471772fe321d970be9acbb0894ddb98ead7fb4","tid":2028460,"uid":263018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T23:48:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85def0f1467bd83b9a08078acd1d3c47e7805c46","tid":2028460,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T04:42:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9679c54dfd0b93beba058e7e584e4021298fd01","tid":2028460,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:22:37.000Z","msg":"而問題係美國會回應<br />\n但中共會唔會放下面子而選擇延遲香港立法時間<br />\n又係另一個問題"},{"pid":"cc1a2a6d0faaded51f4257d7dc6dbf455c30b542","tid":2028460,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:57:06.000Z","msg":"毒撚冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7042feee616b43362ae18ca77bdc080e5676d5b","tid":2028460,"uid":196712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T07:00:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"acc296c55e755e68e2d8a1c9895a0230e0413dfb","tid":2028460,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7042feee616b43362ae18ca77bdc080e5676d5b","tid":2028460,"uid":196712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T07:00:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T07:01:17.000Z","msg":"最快半年後執行"},{"pid":"0e6578e3f6ea55ec23019